race.comment: FRANKFURT (1) is hard to catch but he finds a suitable assignment and assess his chances an the near miss at Darwin two back. Has been kept on the fresh side and has won over the mile. MURRAJONG ROAD (4) has threatened here his last two and gets in well with the 3kg claim. Has the winkers on again and has recorded a win at the trip. Will go close in a weak contest. PROPHESIER (5) mixes the form but would have claims putting his best foot forward. Should be around the mark. MIRACOLI (3) has been freshened off consecutive placings at Kununurra. BECQUEREL (7) next elect. Resumed with a placing last start at this course and now gets out to a mile.
